{"tid":518429,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★蘋果流年不利？10 周年機銷量毫無起色遭外資睇死！","createTime":"2018-01-03T10:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T11:30:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"509f6c3d3c016f80743464039bf26fbc8d6e93c5","tid":518429,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:12:44.000Z","msg":"2018-01-03<br />\n<br />\n當日前傳出蘋果的生產線已經減產 iPhone X 的數量，最大原因當然是 iPhone X 的銷量不如理想，由原定的 5,000 萬部下調至 3,000 萬部，當認為這是最底數的時候，原來不幸還會接踵而來，有關消息慘遭美外資偷笑，認為蘋果預算 3,000 萬部已足夠的多，股價亦過於睇高，所以唯一認同的是 iPhone X 銷量不似如期的說法。<br />\n<br />\n從報告中可見，2017 年的第 4 季 iPhone X 銷量只有 3,000 萬至 3,500 萬部，而在 2018 年第一季，又沒有利好消息下，難以想像 iPhone X 的銷量可以突破 3000 萬這個數字，反而連維持都有一定壓力。由於推出至今已經一段時間，想直接換機的客戶一早就已經更換，而且蘋果亦有可能採取減價策略，以測試消費者的消費能力及慾望，似乎外資的預測比起蘋果的預期更有說服力呢！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://pc3mag.com/apple-iphone-x-reduce-sales/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fapple-iphone-x-reduce-sales%2F&d=ryJDW5LW9OMZ1e8iLawrI5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=2471aa8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://pc3mag.com/apple-iphone-x-reduce-sales/</a>"},{"pid":"3fc7d7b5cf29bfa7bbdac4d7629a45d663b6881c","tid":518429,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaac117910a5cbb6cd92b57d5fe3d67aaf44912a","tid":518429,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"蘋果已死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bb64009848bc1d15bf5dce08083d34f2a91276","tid":518429,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaac117910a5cbb6cd92b57d5fe3d67aaf44912a","tid":518429,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T11:16:30.000Z